## 📦 VERSION MANAGEMENT (required at every task)

Single source of truth: the app semver lives only in package.json under "version".

At the end of every task that ships a version bump:

1. Update "version" in package.json (semver: patch per small change, minor for feature groups, major for breaking redesigns).
2. Run npm install at the repo root so package-lock.json stays aligned.
3. Commit the lockfile if it changed.

Do not maintain lib/version.ts or APP_VERSION (one source only).

## 🔔 TASK COMPLETION
After completing ANY task, always end your final message with:
"✅ DONE — Check required"

## 🔁 VERPLICHTE WORKFLOW (ALTIJD VOLGEN)

Na elke taak:
1. Genereer wijzigingen (Cursor)
2. Test lokaal EERST (localhost:3000)
3. Keep All PAS NA testen
4. Commit DAARNA naar GitHub
5. Dan pas verder naar volgende taak

NOOIT: Keep All zonder testen
NOOIT: Committen zonder testen
NOOIT: Volgende blok starten zonder vorige te testen

## 🚀 WORKFLOW (always follow — every session)

1. Pull first
   git pull origin main

2. Snapshot (only if uncommitted work exists)
   git add .
   git commit -m "vX.Y.Z chore: Snapshot before [taskname]"
   git push origin main

3. Cursor builds (Plan Mode → review → Accept All)

4. Test locally
   npm run dev → open localhost:3000

5. Commit + push
   git add .
   git commit -m "vX.Y.Z type(scope): Description"
   git push origin main

## 🔁 BRANCH RULE — CRITICAL
- ALWAYS work on main — never create a dev branch
- If you find yourself on a branch other than main, run:
  git checkout main
  git merge [branchname]
  git push origin main

